OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,FA cancer patient who had the wrong rib
OL,7,Fremoved by surgeons has been awarded
OL,8,F"substantial damages" from the
OL,9,Fhospital responsible.
OL,11,FThe woman, who has not been named, was
OL,12,Fadmitted to Castle Hill Hospital, in
OL,13,FCottingham, near Hull, for an
OL,14,Foperation in 2017 after scans showed a
OL,15,Fpotentially cancerous growth on her
OL,16,Fseventh rib.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
