OL,3,CSurgeons removed wrong rib from cancer
OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,FBut two weeks later she was told that
OL,7,Fher entire sixth rib had been removed
OL,8,Fby mistake and that she would need
OL,9,Fanother operation to remove the
OL,10,Fcorrect one.
OL,12,FShe said: "When I was told that they'd
OL,13,Ftaken out the wrong rib I was in
OL,14,Fcomplete disbelief and I just said to
OL,15,Fthe surgeon, 'you must be joking'.
OL,17,F"I remember the surgeon being very
OL,18,Fblase about it, and even making a
OL,19,Fcomment about not making the same
OL,20,Fmistake again as he'd have more space
OL,21,Fto work in the second time around.
OL,26,@zD@Err
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
