PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F362A1734440347
OL,3,CSurgeons removed wrong rib from cancer
OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,F"My husband is usually a really placid
OL,7,Fman, but he was furious at how the
OL,8,Fsurgeon showed a lack of care, concern
OL,9,Fand compassion. It was like it wasn't
OL,10,Fa big deal, and he was trying to play
OL,11,Fdown the seriousness of it all."
OL,13,FThe patient, of East Yorkshire, had
OL,14,Fbeen suffering from worsening chest
OL,15,Fpains and a cough for someJtime, so
OL,16,Fmuch so it was impacting on her
OL,17,Fquality of life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
