OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,FFollowing the second procedure in
OL,7,FOctober 2017, the woman said she had
OL,8,Fsuffered from chronic chest pains and
OL,9,Fhad to quit her job as a healthcare
OL,10,Fassistant.
OL,12,FHer husband took voluntary redundancy
OL,13,Fto care for her. The couple have spent
OL,14,Fmost of their time living in their
OL,15,Fstatic home on a caravan site as she
OL,16,Fstruggles to walk up stairs.
OL,18,F'Completely unavoidable'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
