OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,FShe said: "The impact of this mistake
OL,7,Fhas been immense on my life, as I have
OL,8,Fgone from being a very healthy and
OL,9,Factive woman to being a bit of a couch
OL,10,Fpotato.
OL,12,F"We used to look after our
OL,13,Fgranddaughter whilst our daughter was
OL,14,Fat work, but again I've found that
OL,15,Fvery difficult and it has been
OL,16,Fheartbreaking not to be able to play
OL,17,Fwith her like I used to.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
