OL,3,CSurgeons removed wrong rib from cancer
OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,F"This has also caused me to fear
OL,7,Fhospitals. I've had to go back for
OL,8,Fother reasons since and I was really
OL,9,Ffearful and not happy to be there at
OL,10,Fall."
OL,12,FThe Hull Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,13,Fadmitted breaching its duty of care
OL,14,Fover the mistake, which is classed as
OL,15,Fa "never event" - an incident which
OL,16,Fshould never happen.
OL,18,FIt agreed "significant" out-of-court
OL,19,Fdamages.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
