OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,FHelena Wood, of Hudgell Solicitors,
OL,7,Fwhich represented the woman said:
OL,8,F"This was a basic, completely
OL,9,Funavoidable error which has had a
OL,10,Fhugely negative impact on my client's
OL,11,Fquality of life.
OL,13,F"Sadly, hundreds of these mistakes are
OL,14,Fbeing made in hospitals each year, in
OL,15,Fsome cases causing seriousJlong-term
OL,16,Fsuffering and harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
