OL,3,CSurgeons removed wrong rib from cancer
OL,4,Cpatient
OL,6,F"These commonly include procedures
OL,7,Fbeing performed on the wrong area of a
OL,8,Fpatient, like happened toJmy client,
OL,9,Fto surgical instruments and swabs
OL,10,Fbeing left inside patients after
OL,11,Fmedical procedures."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for NHS Humber Health
OL,14,FPartnership said: "Our aim is always
OL,15,Fto provide the highest possible
OL,16,Fstandards of patient care, and we
OL,17,Fdeeply regret that, on this occasion,
OL,18,Fthose standards were not met.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
